Features Summary
For TI-83 Plus and TI-84 Plus graphing calculators
Within seconds, educators can gain control over testing environments using TI TestGuard 2.0 to:

  * Remove or disable programs and applications on student calculators before tests
  * Delete other data stored on student calculators before tests
  * Restore programs and applications on student calculators after test
